nodes.text: The Cardooine system was located in the Outer Rim's Jospro sector. It contained the planet Cardooine.

Cardooine was where the Rebel Alliance built A-wings used in the Battle of Endor. It was also the home of Fijisi wood, used in sections of the Imperial Palace on Coruscant and other high-class buildings.
The disease Cardooine Chills originated within this system.
